### AnsibleTower ###
# Ansible runtime and backups
*.original
*.tmp
*.bkp
*.retry
*.*~

# Tower runtime roles
roles/**
!roles/requirements.yml

# Avoid plain-text passwords
*pwd*
*pass*
*password*
*.txt

# Exclude all binaries
*.bin
*.jar
*.tar
*.zip
*.gzip
*.tgz

### Secret ###
